location.fullValue: Glimmer Plan, Pender Woods at Cane Bay

data.description: ASSUMABLE 4.75% VA LOAN WITH VA ELIGIBLE QUALIFICATION!! This is a SMART home design.  The first floor features an open living design with a large kitchen island and eat-in kitchen. Upstairs features a spacious master bedroom with a large walk-in closet that has a master bath with a dual sink vanity and large stand up shower. The 2nd  & 3rd bedrooms upstairs are also spacious with walk-in closets.  The tankless gas hot water heater will have endless hot water. There is a a resort style water park, playground, and sidewalks along with Cane Bay that has walking & golf cart trails & YMCA. It located 10 minutes to Volvo, 20 minutes to Joint Base Charleston (USN) ,30 minutes to Joint Base Charleston (USAF), 40 minutes to downtown Charleston and all beaches. Cypress Gardens and Bushy Park isabout 20 minutes as well for fresh and salt water access. The YMCA that is in Cane Bay has a membership available for all Cane Bay neighborhood residents. The large water park in Pine Hills also has an open air pavilion with eight picnic tables under a roof lit with ceiling fans. Berkeley Preparatory School is located outside the back entrance into Pine Hills off Black Tom Rd at 122 Bee Tree Blvd. This is a must see home and neighborhood!! This is truly a family neighborhood with these amazing amenities!!
